item.description:
Reversed World 2014 is now out here: https://soundcloud.com/peter-brev/peter-b-reversed-world-2014

Downloadable here (Get it here): https://mega.co.nz/#!rhg2zCLS!O3ASNDKwT55MyP-LAV7A5CqaSkZmo33bRrVRClDYRcU

I recommend using the download link here instead of sound cloud one, just as an advice.

Tracklist is on SoundCloud, but I’ll post it here too:

  1. Blackout - I Am The Darkness
  2. Dany BPM - Life the Moment
  3. DJ Eos - Melody of Dope
  4. Alpha Protocol - Let Yourself Go
  5. Jacky Core - Samouraï
  6. Lethal MG - The Holy Grail (Karl F Remix)
  7. Roman Klash - On Beat
  8. Teka B and Ron S - Creampie
  9. Killer Traxx - House Party
  10. DJ Seb B & Carnaby - Alarmatagueule
  11. Activator - Summer Breeze
  12. Audiofreq - Gotta Have Ya Love (Festuca Edit)
  13. In-Phase - Here We Go
  14. Zatox & Hit ‘n’ Run - Never More
  15. Toneshiterz - R.A.W. Power
  16. Wild Motherfuckers - Wild Wild West
  17. DJ Deeon - House of matic ( Spektrum 7 remix )
  18. Showtek - FTS (Peacekeeper Edit)
  19. Scope DJ - Lockdown (2013 Live Edit)
  20. Safri Duo - Samb-Adagio (Star Driver’s Hardstyle Remix)

You’ll notice the differences between the first compilation and this one, improved alot, haven’t I?

Also, check my YouTube channel because I also upload the mixes here as well: https://www.youtube.com/user/MIXPeterB/videos
